  "body": "Originally was fixed in #3112 but seems we have issues again. I tested it in `Build #1299 (02-Sep-2021 20:23:16) ` having `Big Sur 11.5.2 (20G95)`\r\n\r\n\r\nUser is logged in\r\n\r\nAction | \"Minimize on close\" set to true | Result | \"Minimize on close\" set to false | Result |\r\n-- | -- | -- | -- | -- |\r\nclose on \"X\" button | minimize | :white_check_mark: | close | it works but #3357\r\nclose on \"Quit\" from the dock | close | :x: **it does not close the app** | close | it works but #3357\r\nclose on \"Signout and Quit\" | close | :white_check_mark: | close | it works but #3357\r\nclose on \"Quit Status\" from the app menu bar | close | it works but #3357 | close | it works but #3357",
